description: The Smoking Cow is making Minnesota proud, with a menu that offers amazingly tasty dishes, all made from fresh, local ingredients. Their delicious burgers are just the start of what you'll find here. With a savory selection of Smoked Goat Legs, Fried Delicata Squash, House Made Mozzarella Sticks, and much more, your appetite will surely be delightedly satisfied. If you wish to try a taste of the hard-working, high-quality spirit that makes Minneapolis so great, then The Smoking Cow is the food truck for you!!
name: The Smoking Cow
